metadata.name: Project Motoyo #1
metadata.description: Project MOTOYO offers unique NFTs blending AI, web3 and anime. Each NFT is one-of-a-kind and verified on blockchain, ensuring authenticity and scarcity. Limited supply of 666 NFTs with potential for appreciation in value. Supporting the art community by providing an opportunity for artists and collectors. Get your piece of the future of digital art with Project MOTOYO.
